  "text": "I'll just uh try to pick up that last question left over from the last session. If uh you can answer it, I don't know if it's of any importance, but it just uh occurred to me that the parts removed in cattle mutilations were the same every time, and I just wondered if this was related to the energy centers and and uh why they they were important if that was so. I am Ra. This is basically correct if you may understand that there is a link between energy centers and various thought forms. Thus the affairs of the amass consciousness create the climate for the concentration upon the removal of bodily parts which symbolize areas of concern or fear in the mass consciousness.",
